parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Airbag System Failure and Recall Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident. Delays or difficulties in repairing or replacing recalled airbag components can leave drivers and passengers at risk.
symptoms: Airbag warning lights or messages
inability to repair or replace recalled airbag components
cracking or damage to the dashboard or airbag casing
airbag failure to deploy in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Dashboard Cracking and Airbag Casing Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cracking or damage to the dashboard or airbag casing can lead to airbag failure or deployment, causing injury or death. Poor manufacturing quality can also lead to other safety issues.
symptoms: Cracking or damage to the dashboard or airbag casing
airbag casing pushing through the dashboard
airbag failure to deploy in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Delays or unavailability of recall repairs can leave drivers and passengers at risk of injury or death due to faulty airbag systems.
symptoms: Inability to repair or replace recalled airbag components
lack of communication from the manufacturer or dealership
delayed or unavailable repair appointments.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to seize or become difficult to maneuver, making it challenging to control the vehicle, especially during turns, which can lead to accidents or near-miss situations.
symptoms: The power steering partially or completely fails
making turns difficult or impossible
the steering wheel seizes or becomes hard to turn
the vehicle pulls to one direction
the power steering failure light comes on
the vehicle creaks or makes unusual noises while steering.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Corrosion of the oil cooler lines can cause oil leaks, leading to environmental hazards, safety risks, and potential engine failure or fires.
symptoms: Oil leaks
rusting or corrosion of oil cooler lines
power steering issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the air conditioning system can cause discomfort and distraction for the driver and passengers, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: Inconsistent or inadequate cooling
AC not blowing cold air
AC not working properly.
